comments: Bryant (WAS) grabs Durant's (BKN) arm during his drive to the basket.
Harris (BKN) clamps Hachimura's (WAS) arm while he is receiving the pass in the post, disrupting his ability to catch the ball cleanly.
Green (BKN) firms up in a screening position in the path of Hachimura (WAS) and absorbs the contact.
Hachimura (WAS) briefly engages and then disengages in marginal arm contact with Durant (BKN) as he is receiving the pass.
Green (BKN) firms up in a screening position in the path of Hachimura (WAS) and absorbs the contact.
Beal (WAS) does not get up to ball height and makes contact to Durant's (BKN) arm as he is in his shooting motion and releases the ball on his jump shot.
Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Irving (BKN) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Green (BKN) makes marginal contact to Beal's (WAS) arm during his shooting motion that does not disrupt his layup attempt.
Beal (WAS) makes marginal contact to Luwawu-Cabarrot's (BKN) body, but does not disrupt his ability to make the pass.
Irving (BKN) firms up in a screening position in the path of Hachimura (WAS) and absorbs the contact.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) makes marginal contact to Bryant's (WAS) arm during his shooting motion that does not disrupt the dunk attempt.
